  <header class="row row-tagline">
    <div class="col-sm-8">
      <h2 class="m-t-0">ONE CLICK BLOCKCHAIN</h2>
      <p>Quickly fire up a personal Ethereum blockchain which you can use to run tests, execute commands, and inspect state while controlling how the chain operates.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="col-sm-4">
      <div class="pull-right">
        <a class="btn btn-orange">
