<div class="container-fluid">
  <section class="row row-features-heading">
    <img class="ganache-goop" src="/images/suite/ganache/ganache-goop.svg" />

    <div class="col-xs-12">
      <h2 class="text-center text-ganache">Features</h2>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>

<div class="container">
  <section class="row row-features">
    <div class="col-sm-6 text-center">
      <img src="/images/suite/ganache/ganache-feature-1-icon.svg" />
      <h3>THE ETHEREUM BLOCKCHAIN</h3>
      <p>Ganache ships with an internal Javascript implementation of the Ethereum Blockchain which has additional programmatic capabilities - no local clients need to be installed!</p>
    </div>

    <div class="col-sm-6 text-center">
      <img src="/images/suite/ganache/ganache-feature-2-icon.svg" />
      <h3>VISUAL MNEMONIC &amp; ACCOUNT INFO</h3>
      <p>Quickly see the current status of the generated accounts, including their addresses, private keys, nonces and balances.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="row row-features">
    <div class="col-sm-6 text-center">
      <img src="/images/suite/ganache/ganache-feature-3-icon.svg" />
      <h3>BLOCKCHAIN LOG OUTPUT</h3>
      <p>See the output of web3 calls to the blockchain, along with responses and other vital debugging information.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="col-sm-6 text-center">
      <img src="/images/suite/ganache/ganache-feature-4-icon.svg" />
      <h3>INSTANT MINING CONTROLS</h3>
      <p>Stop, start, force mine a single block, and take or revert multiple snapshots of the blockchain as and when you chose.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="row row-features">
    <div class="col-sm-6 text-center">
      <img src="/images/suite/ganache/ganache-feature-5-icon.svg" />
      <h3>BUILT-IN BLOCK EXPLORER</h3>
      <p>Examine specific blocks or transactions at will and see detailed information about the parameters.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="col-sm-6 text-center">
      <img src="/images/suite/ganache/ganache-feature-6-icon.svg" />
      <h3>BLOCKCHAIN CONNECTED CONSOLE</h3>
      <p>Access a Node.js powered Console to execute commands, with a fully initialized instance of web3, and many useful commands to make development and testing easy.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="row row-features-bottom">
    <div class="col-xs-12 text-center">
      <a class="btn btn-orange">
        <span class="oswald">DOWNLOAD</span></br>
        <span class="os">(Windows)</span>
        <img src="/images/suite/ganache/windows-logo.svg" />
      </a>
      <p class="os-dl"><a href="https://github.com/trufflesuite/ganache/releases">Need a different OS download?</a></p>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>

